Q: update an application which was developed in an old version of kubernetes

k explain deployment.spec

k explain deployment.spec.selector

vi /ckad/credible-mite/www.yaml

update version, namespace name, add selector.matchLabels
the value under deployment.spec.selector.matchLabels should be the same as the one under deployment.spec.template.metadata.labels

k apply -f /ckad/credible-mite/www.yaml 

//verify
k -n garfish get deployment
k -n garfish get pod
